Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忘记的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我们俩要再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都写完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能心无旁骛的去谷川岳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵超级有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 约定实现了 会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(269,549)}「去往回忆中的大山」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到这一天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 富士山都登过了 还怕这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定实现了 会有什么改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会又在登山途中不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我睡得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会因此有什么结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高崎站换乘上越线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再在水上站换乘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计在10时左右到达土合站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然从水上站那里乘巴士很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是从土合站那里是登山的路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从站台到车站出口有条非常长的台阶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 感觉以前好像登过台阶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以不只是因为那里是路 我想从那里开始登山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站台竟然是这样的隧道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 多少记得点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷飕飕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台阶是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说有四百阶以上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你也记得？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 可能比印象中更多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台阶就像登山一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会延伸到哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是热身了 慢慢来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不能在这种地方就精疲力尽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是要登上谷川岳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不多用点体力可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 老婆子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是老婆子啊 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟 嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟 嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟 嘿哟 嘿哟 嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,460
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,461
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,462
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到检票出口还有143米 两处台阶共24阶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们写什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山登记哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇难的时候警察可以用上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇 遇难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一 要写上何时去哪里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系方式 路线 和下山预定时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写的真详细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点麻烦 但是得好好写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想死呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的到回忆中的大山来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气不错太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大山的天气说变就变 不可大意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了雨具没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说我反而想让它下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这种不吉利的话 会看不到日出的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了 刚才的不算 不算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有小卖店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要买东西的话回程的时候再买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要小群马周边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小群马？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和梦马非常像非常可爱的马儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵想要买什么样的礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 没事哦 完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色铁青
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她果然很害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 加油吧 还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起三增峠的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵不会在这种地方止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 向上看 我们接下来要登上那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了 太好了 太好了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 说做就能做到啊葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了 枫 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你努力了呢 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你第一关通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 第二关在等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 还有上山吊椅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缆车都已经通关了 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都 都没有遮挡的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没有缆车那么高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么高啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起的话 可以超越困难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 向更前方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我们约定的地方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
